      • SPOStarJoin

        public SPOStarJoin(SPOPredicate pred)
        Construct an SPO star join from a normal SPO predicate. The star join will have a triple pattern of (S,?,?) instead of the (S,P,O) from the original SPO predicate. This way all SPOs for the common subject are considered. SPO star constraints must be added later to make this star join selective.
        Parameters:
        pred - the normal SPO predicate from which to pull the S
